  "note": "S-COMPOSE-CALM slice 3, P7 Multi-Instrument Maestro goalpost (design table: 'switches profiles mid-thought; per-profile voicings; silence is the reward') + UAT r5 F5 (operator 2026-07-19: Shapes off the Compose surface; chord-chart visibility is a Settings > Preferences choice - Dots|Patterns stays, it styles diagrams, different job). Fixture: advanced + an in-flight uke draft. Journey: uke Compose lands dense and silent with NO Shapes chip; Save knows the uke draft; the maestro flips Chord charts -> Charts in Settings (4-string uke voicings appear); switches to guitar mid-thought; guitar keeps the advanced level AND the charts preference (both are global - 'profile switch persists'), draws 6-string voicings, and Save sees a FRESH side (per-profile draft separation). Zero tips anywhere.",
  "viewport": {
    "width": 412,
    "height": 915
  },
  "steps": [
    {
